Given I'm logged-in with valid credentials
When I select 'Female' radio button from Page 01 of Pelvic MRI
And I select 'MRI pelvic floor' radio button from Page 01 of Pelvic MRI
Then I go to Page 08 of Pelvic MRI
And I click on 'Finding' radio button
And dropdown below 'Finding' is enabled

When I select 'Sigmoid volvulus' from the dropdown
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled

And 'Coffee bean sign' checkbox is enabled
And 'Whirl sign' checkbox is enabled
And 'Free perforation' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ascites' checkbox is enabled

And 'Maximum dilatation' input field is enabled

When I enter '1' in the input field below 'Maximum dilatation' checkbox
Then the number is accepted
When I enter '9999' in the input field below 'Maximum dilatation' checkbox
Then the number is accepted
